        "short_description": "Do whatever you want in a physics sandbox full of chaotic destruction, endless player-made creations and unpredictable adventures. Build, destroy, roleplay and mess around solo or with friends!",
        "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/6db18538f401c350772a7a9ad0ff1325.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/28ed08d232ad74f752ea4e86677e89d3.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/28ed08d232ad74f752ea4e86677e89d3.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/28ed08d232ad74f752ea4e86677e89d3.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Brick Rigs, you can become anything: a firefighter racing to the scene, a pilot in intense aerial combat, or a police officer in a high‑speed chase. Build, play, experiment, destroy. You decide what, and how, you want to play. The only rule is that it has to be fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/2dc48196e6f24352804613bfe3f94838.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=124 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/a8641e87e0e9cdb80744213bb2b26aa0.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/a8641e87e0e9cdb80744213bb2b26aa0.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/a8641e87e0e9cdb80744213bb2b26aa0.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your own vehicles, machines, creatures, or buildings. In the Brick Rigs Editor, there are no limits to your imagination. Ever dreamed of a flying submarine? With a little patience, you can build almost anything and try it out directly in the game. The powerful editor lets you create detailed models with realistic, functional mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/be2878d811209d644f590d7ad7dcf47a.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=184 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/30c1384de38dcbf0902b69bc516d170d.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/30c1384de38dcbf0902b69bc516d170d.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/30c1384de38dcbf0902b69bc516d170d.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>No patience to build your own vehicle? No problem. Ambitious Brick Rigs players have already filled the Workshop with a whole universe of fantastic builds. From detailed minivans to giant transport planes and entire skyscrapers, there's something for everyone. Discover it all now in the Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/b7c1f31d6ca3864c38ad23238d024449.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=124 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/995110b559641b92293607fe76713850.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/995110b559641b92293607fe76713850.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/995110b559641b92293607fe76713850.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Yes, building your own vehicles is really fun. But let's be honest — destroying them is just as much fun. With dynamic destruction physics, every crash looks especially spectacular. See how far you can make those bricks fly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/8dec6d135eb6c77f937e740382e6a4e8.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=121 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/db1342fd0d2a7b470c1ca2698a8b6a54.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/db1342fd0d2a7b470c1ca2698a8b6a54.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/db1342fd0d2a7b470c1ca2698a8b6a54.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Brick Rigs has a large, passionate community. Play with friends, team up, or experiment on your own.<br>From roleplay servers and high-speed chases to massive multiplayer chaos, players are constantly creating new ways to play.<br>Anything is possible in Brick Rigs — as long as you're having fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/5ae234b6b6de3881755e3642966054f5.avif?t=1780405668\" width=780 height=109 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/c47d5205b1ba9e04722dbb51465be8e6.poster.avif?t=1780405668\" width=1170 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/c47d5205b1ba9e04722dbb51465be8e6.webm?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/552100/extras/c47d5205b1ba9e04722dbb51465be8e6.mp4?t=1780405668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bob is the face of Brick Rigs. He's been there from the very beginning and has experienced a lot: adventures, disasters, parties, and much more. And what can Bob actually do? Pretty much nothing. But he's a really lovable guy.",
